DialogLines = Array[String](["Frank: Oh — a new cellmate. Name's Frank. I've been in this cell longer than the wallpaper.", "Layout? Cell Block C is past the north door. Guard room's got the key. Don't ask how I know.", "Block A's collapsed. Block B's where they keep the noisy ones. The kitchen's through the west hall — if you smell oatmeal, you've gone too far.", "There's a book around here somewhere — 'Eggs Isle: A History.' Boring, but the warden quizzes everyone who wants out. Read it. Trust me.", "Me? I'm not going anywhere. Someone has to keep the moss company."])
